The paper discusses the comparison and performance analysis of open source machine learning frameworks for various parameters, including neural network architectures and activation functions, for image recognition problems. This falls under the categories of machine learning (cs.LG), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), computer vision (cs.CV), neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE), and distributed, parallel, and cluster computing (cs.DC).
